rows.label: tev021901_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Coco about the coffee situation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Coco if she has any interesting news.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Coco about Jo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0001
rows.name:
The coffee beans that are being made at the integrated
production plant have really improved in quality lately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0002
rows.name:
Nevertheless, I'd kill to get my hands on some real
Miran-grown beans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0003
rows.name:
Doesn't the prospect of a new type of coffee that could
only be found on this remote world excite you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0004
rows.name:
Of course, I don't know if this planet even has an
equivalent for Earth's coffee plant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0005
rows.name:
But if they keep expanding FrontierNav,
we'll learn the answer soon enough, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0006
rows.name:
Anyway, establishing a new Miran-exclusive line of
products is another great reason to get out there and
install those data probes![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0007
rows.name:
I'm counting on you! And if all that hard work tires
you out, you can always come visit my shop to kick
back and relax.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0010
rows.name:
There's a researcher named Sullivan who's a regular
here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0011
rows.name:
Whenever she comes in, all she does is complain about
how she doesn't have enough "samples" or something.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0012
rows.name:
Anyway, I remembered how you helped out poor Jo,
and was thinking maybe you could give Sullivan a
hand next?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0013
rows.name:
You can find her at the integrated production plant
in the industrial district. Drop in and hear her out
sometime![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0022
rows.name:
Some of our regulars have started wagering on what
Jo will break next.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0023
rows.name:
It's driving me nuts. I tell them there's nothing funny
about it, but they seem to enjoy studying her every
move.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0024
rows.name:
In the end, they took the money they'd made wagering
and bought me a replacement for something Jo broke.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0025
rows.name:
I really appreciated the thought, but as the owner,
I have mixed feelings about my customers cheering
accidental wanton destruction.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0026
rows.name:
Now that poor Jo has her own legion of fans,
god only knows what's going to befall this shop next.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Coco about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0027
rows.name:
I heard you helped out Sullivan! Thank you so much.
...Kind of an odd duck, though, isn't she?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0028
rows.name:
She said something about display samples and bonus
samples and... Well, I could barely follow it.
Regardless, she left an extra sample here with me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0029
rows.name:
She said it was a something-or-other seeder?
...Or did she mean cedar? Like, as in the tree?
Geez, I hope it won't trigger anyone's allergies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0030
rows.name:
Jo used to have terrible allergies, which really affected
the rate at which she broke stuff. But the whole
mimeosome thing took care of that for her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021901_MSG0031
rows.name:
Honestly, I still haven't gotten used to being inside an
artificial body. It just feels a bit...strange.[ST:wait ]
